{"tid":2399730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專上學歷失業率8.9% 平均120日冇工開  多12萬家庭跌入貧窮線","createTime":"2021-02-08T11:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T11:34:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbd4e96bb566f86bca6d4b94303f8c8e1179a07","tid":2399730,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210208/UTJMWCLX6JGDXKE7ZARIYD3DIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210208%2FUTJMWCLX6JGDXKE7ZARIYD3DIU%2F&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUigOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=4ee0e831\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210208%2FUTJMWCLX6JGDXKE7ZARIYD3DIU%2F&h=589ad942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210208/UTJMWCLX6JGDXKE7ZARIYD3DIU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n專上學歷失業率8.9% 平均120日冇工開 <br />\n多12萬家庭跌入貧窮線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vXhZNrlGp-Kybv1Ns5uVooBMEZ8=/2263x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BXIQDGZ3CZGA7DPJ3VVOWYVIWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvXhZNrlGp-Kybv1Ns5uVooBMEZ8%3D%2F2263x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBXIQDGZ3CZGA7DPJ3VVOWYVIWI.jpg&h=66c507d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■武漢肺炎疫情重創經濟，不少打工仔面臨失業困境。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】疫情重創各行各業，不少打工仔淪為失業大軍。社聯發現超過30%失業及就業不足的家庭陷入貧窮，若以學歷劃分，具專上教育文憑學歷人士的失業率高達8.9%，高於小學和中學學歷人士。社聯總監黃健偉表示，中或高等職位人士失業時間中位數超過120天，家庭收入減幅平均逾五成。有人力資源顧問指經濟不景時，公司裁減中層職位的成本效益較高，有關人士轉行或需面對較大的人工減幅。<br />\n<br />\n社聯分析去年第三季就業數據，失業率為6.4%，近26萬人失業。社聯總主任（政策研究及倡議）黃和平表示，失業情況不限於低學歷人士，小學、中學以至專上教育程度人士的失業率均超過8%，其中具專上教育文憑學歷人士失業率更高達8.9%，高於其他較低學歷人士。<br />\n<br />\n部份中層職位失業情況嚴重。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n社聯總監黃健偉指，中或高職位。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/r-ZAsCmxSTA6P7idu57Vt1yXtv8=/1338x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3QECEK6GNJH6JIVQN2EACECGJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fr-ZAsCmxSTA6P7idu57Vt1yXtv8%3D%2F1338x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3QECEK6GNJH6JIVQN2EACECGJA.jpg&h=323d6eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃健偉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n社聯倡設失業保險制度<br />\n<br />\n失業情況嚴峻，黃健偉稱，本港17.1%從事經濟活動的家庭最少有一名成員面對失業或就業不足，涉及近36萬個家庭，當中超過12.3萬個家庭、即34.1%家庭收入低於貧窮線。<br />\n<br />\n黃健偉指，不少家庭未必合資格申請綜援，只有5.3%的失業及就業不足人士正領取綜援，建議政府設立短期失業援助，以及放寬在職家庭津貼申請資格，將最低工時要求由72小時下調至36小時，同時向所有合資格領取全額職津家庭發放雙倍津貼。他建議政府研究失業保險制度，協助不同階層人士在失業期間維持穩定生活。<br />\n<br />\n合眾人事顧問有限公司總經理蘇偉忠。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n安俊人力資源顧問董事總經理周綺萍指，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"ab5eef585aa244679aee588444c5eb141f92d606","tid":2399730,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:20:43.000Z","msg":"一個癲婆，害700幾萬人同佢癲，700幾萬人同佢癲呀！"},{"pid":"69e876b862ea0f3a6af66d8af20156d6d4824669","tid":2399730,"uid":61032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:21:59.000Z","msg":"降低條貧窮線咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c405bf1a2a85a0d81f7974c91785a69d63ab21f0","tid":2399730,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:24:48.000Z","msg":"派錢啦屌佢老母"},{"pid":"f8d026e7e578bbcf03e7d62843fa5654a431a0b3","tid":2399730,"uid":128417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:34:26.000Z","msg":"點解冇晒反對派都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}